  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <name>Flatland</name>
  <summary>Virtual displays for desktop apps</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
    	Panel shell (like a window manager) for Stardust XR that puts 2D apps inside flat slabs with resize handles.
    </p>
    <p>
    	You're meant to leave them around your space, walking around (not seated).
    </p>
  </description>
